posterior face of protibia. 2. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="" authorityYear="1970" baseAuthorityName="Schedl" box="[916,1179,673,695]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Dinoxyleborus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="133" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sexnotatus">
<emphasis box="[916,1179,673,695]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="133">Dinoxyleborus sexnotatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
antennal club.
</paragraph>
